# Ralph reviewer — one senior-review pass at :13 and :43 past every hour.
# Install with:  crontab -e   (paste the line below)
# Appends to ~/review-board.log. SHADOW mode by default (no auto-merge).
13,43 * * * * /home/div/.local/bin/review-board

# Ralph worker — autonomous pickup, SCOPED TO REP-SHEET ONLY (work-board's jq filter).
# Runs at :00 and :30 so a freshly-opened PR meets the reviewer pass ~13 min later.
# Appends to ~/work-board.log. Once enabled, every Ready-for-Agent card on rep-sheet is
# a live trigger — start here, slow the schedule (or unfilter to add repos) as needed.
0,30 * * * * /home/div/.local/bin/work-board
